### Arabic

<span style="display: block; font-size: 180%; text-align: right;">وَإِذَآ أَنْعَمْنَا عَلَى ٱلْإِنسَـٰنِ أَعْرَضَ وَنَـَٔا بِجَانِبِهِۦ ۖ وَإِذَا مَسَّهُ ٱلشَّرُّ كَانَ يَـُٔوسًا</span>

### English

When We grant people Our favours, they turn away, acting arrogantly. But when touched with evil, they lose all hope.